{"tid":126943,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女朋友冇咩野講","createTime":"2017-02-19T17:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T15:16:21.000Z","uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec8704bf48c9961859b1ddfe9aa3ed257d810353","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"同佢好多野都唔係好合<br />\n好多時一齊就冇野講，有時見到佢同其他男仔好多野傾，會覺得自己係唔係真係適合佢。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔關帽唔帽事，純粹覺得好似唔多合"},{"pid":"395c356db78f95d5695483cba2e1481a6588a5e6","tid":126943,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"有冇打算同佢傾吓呢個問題，以前同ex一齊都係咁，我地本來係一大班fd嚟所以同啲男仔都好熟識咗好多年。嗰陣佢成日都覺得我同啲男仔fd多嘢傾啲開心啲好妒忌，後來我地有傾過呢個問題，慢慢磨合到適合嘅相處方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣我說發現，其實有時只要大家相處得舒服，唔需要好多話題好多嘢適講，最緊要你想同佢一齊，靜靜地都可以好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同現任好多嘢講，乜都可以講一餐，有時都唔係有好特定嘅話題，係講啲勁無聊嘅廢話同互相派下膠笑笑下咁就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時喺whatsapp都會講到冇話題，結果我地就喺到互send emoji同廢圖，都唔會覺得悶（利申熱戀）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重要都係有心去相處姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cba9ab9dbec1725d97bf21bbc5ed34e91c6710d","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:08:03.000Z","msg":"但你地最後都係散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講過佢話冇野，但我覺得拍拖同唔到佢分享開心既野，感覺好差。<br />\n同埋佢一同其他朋友傾偈，就好似唔記得左我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954de7126d3ee4a7af944d1c4dea4184c016c363","tid":126943,"uid":9188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:10:15.000Z","msg":"我ex寧願同其他朋友傾計都唔會搵我<br />\n佢話呢個係佢性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係好需要同自己鍾意既人溝通<br />\n最後決定都係做番朋友算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b167327b92a4f8b7ae078952d49ab4618a3c5ec3","tid":126943,"uid":39317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:10:34.000Z","msg":"不如試下一齊去旅行<br />\n搵返d共同話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8e8c3605576330e2e97632ac91e1e1259b82cc","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:13:02.000Z","msg":"我果個都係咁<br />\n寧願同佢啲朋友傾，好似冇咩興趣同我傾咁。我地真係冇咩共同話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afca5feecdc58e5714f31712a032d7f07d4487f6","tid":126943,"uid":71648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:24:18.000Z","msg":"同ex都係咁<br />\n佢成撚日同我講政治<br />\n返實習我已經好攰命要同佢critical thinking係度討論<br />\n成日好認真 講笑都成日起撚哂鋼咁 <br />\n散左好多都散唔到<br />\n最後分手個陣佢話<br />\n認真係因為唔想我認為佢係啲玩玩下既人<br />\nDllm第一次拍拖就咁辛苦真係好有陰影<br />\n我見都唔想見佢 諗話題 扮開心 keep住講真係好撚攰<br />\n<br />\n都係想講 夾既話2個人唔會冇野講 就算冇野講都唔會悶"},{"pid":"3e1afe74c30538c95fbf4382647f46e81ad8634d","tid":126943,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"我都係 份人比較悶 又驚係咁講無聊野對方會介意、覺得無營養<br />\n以前都比ex投訴過少同佢傾心事 淨係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我連同女友行山都有d驚 因為長時間兩個人又沿途無乜野做到話題<br />\n<br />\n不過現任話諗唔到野講可以唔講 完全ok 又話佢都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以到最後都係大家性格夾最緊要"},{"pid":"a1e4f5be2720c1638da4892d5a5dbf84dda1de60","tid":126943,"uid":35888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係 份人比較悶 又驚係咁講無聊野對方會介意、覺得無營養<br />\n以前都比ex投訴過少同佢傾心事 淨係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我連同女友行山都有d驚 因為長時間兩個人又沿途無乜野做到話題<br />\n<br />\n不過現任話<span style=\"color: red;\">諗唔到野講可以唔講 完全ok </span>又話佢都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以到最後都係大家性格夾最緊要</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ee950a4de368835b3f0a865b6d6fe487cbc08b","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:39:25.000Z","msg":"好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91ce94b50b433451d8a0c5a31d52faaeaa3efb2","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"我成日都覺得係唔係自己問題，講野唔好笑，提唔起佢興趣同我講野。<br />\n我以為男女朋友之間有咩開心唔開心都會第一時間同對方講，但原來好似唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6784b3dff1a789c0b515ad31a6db15d70a0c7d8","tid":126943,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:45:43.000Z","msg":"兩個人一齊一定要雞啄唔斷咁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靜得黎感覺舒服自然咪得，其實都係人夾人"},{"pid":"a3dd21605be3b21e65e8afbfaadde7a7e718105e","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T19:24:12.000Z","msg":"問題唔係雞啄唔斷，係女朋友有開心野寧願同其他人分享，但對住你剩係會講自己有幾咁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c796c96ff29400fcaa4555494586be7cef315b9a","tid":126943,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T19:31:43.000Z","msg":"辣殺<br />\n利申 同條條女都可以談天說地"},{"pid":"1e3648f5f9b28784a8ebfe08eb049e528c1f466e","tid":126943,"uid":46514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但你地最後都係散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講過佢話冇野，但我覺得拍拖同唔到佢分享開心既野，感覺好差。<br />\n同埋佢一同其他朋友傾偈，就好似唔記得左我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁分手都可以係其他理由，同我地相處無關，可以話喺大家最愛對方嘅時候分開。<br />\n其實我覺得正正係因為你係最親密嘅人先會願意同你講唔開心嘅事，喺其他人面前可能講唔出呢啲，願意敞開心扉唔係好事咩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你係唔鍾意條女同你講心事，只係想同佢講開心野聽佢講開心野，咁你地嘅感情永遠都只會停留喺好淺層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人喺冇可能永遠都開心。反過嚟睇如果佢淨係同你嘻嘻哈哈，有咩唔開心諗咩都同人講而唔慣同你講先更加大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6f097d3d504cda412040f9af15ec80246f0d8a","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"其他人叫佢幫手，佢會衝住去。我叫佢就好似好唔耐煩，我覺得佢好想討好其他人，但忽略左我"},{"pid":"ab76e897f532aca4bb27dda059de761ea2fb9a30","tid":126943,"uid":70561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63ea340a63861bff5b5171d9cbef1610e38c8d3d","tid":126943,"uid":83767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小小共同話題都無？"},{"pid":"e55f698533ea1587bdabf0579466d8e4af24c012","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"冇，我最在意既係佢在乎其他人既感受，多過在乎我。"},{"pid":"1d5018c605d5e875817235c114e0e2c06c847c6e","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我ex寧願同其他朋友傾計都唔會搵我<br />\n佢話呢個係佢性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係好需要同自己鍾意既人溝通<br />\n最後決定都係做番朋友算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚我地都會變成咁"},{"pid":"c7478cd8c7358e01260856e7e82c370c99d05ce2","tid":126943,"uid":85947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc